highlights.text: Cup of Joe has the most spots on Top Songs Philippines. “Multo” is the highest at #1.
“Higa” by Arthur Nery has been on Top Songs Philippines the longest, at 1935 days straight.
“Gusto Ko Sakin Ka Lang” by Robledo Timido is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Philippines, up 58 spots at #74.
“Sugar On My Tongue” by Tyler, The Creator is the highest new entry on Top Songs Philippines at #174.
